headline: Essex Property Trust Named a Best Company to Work For by U.S. News & World Report
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., May 29, 2025--Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) announced today that it was named a 2025-2026 Best Company to Work For by U.S. News & World Report. Additionally, the Company was named a Best Company to Work For in Real Estate and Facilities Management and a Best Company to Work For in the West. The Company’s recognition can be found here.
